data.description: In a rare opportunity to purchase a former Drees model home, elegance meets functionality in the sprawling Brookdale II floor plan. Professionally curated with luxurious furnishings (available for purchase), the open concept living space boasts high ceilings throughout. The lavish kitchen features a captivating waterfall island, farmhouse sink, and butler's pantry with upgraded built-in appliances. Enjoy the fully furnished home with high-end appliances, two covered patios, and an outdoor kitchen. The main level hosts the primary bedroom with a spa-like en-suite bath, a guest bedroom, full bathroom, and a study. Upstairs, find a game room, media room, and two secondary bedrooms with dedicated full baths. With three living spaces, a study, three-car garage, and RH-inspired design, this home is a haven of sophistication for even the most discerning tastes.
